# 12-logging-monitoring-rules.mdc

---
description: Logging standards
---

Logs must be:

- Structured
- Searchable
- Contextual

Track:

- Authentication events
- Authorization failures
- Payments
- Bookings
- Admin actions
- Integration failures
- Exceptions

Never log:

- Passwords
- Tokens
- Private information
